{{gherdëina}}[[File:Emperor_by_Ivan_Makarov.jpg|thumb|Aculienza dl zar de la [[Ruscia]] tl [[Cremlin de Moscau]].]]'''Zar''' ie n titul che te la storia à abù monarchs te i paejes slavs de l'est. La parola vën dal [[latin]] ''caesar''<ref name=eponym>{{cite web|url=http://www.etymonline.com/index.php?term=tsar|title=Online Etymology Dictionary|work=etymonline.com}}</ref> , sciche ënghe la parola [[lingaz tudësch|tudëscia]] ''Kaiser'', na parola che tl [[Medieve]] univa adurveda per n reniant cun la medema posizion sciche n [[Mper Roman|mperadëur roman]].

L titul ''Zar'' ova abù i monarchs te chisc paejes:
* [[Mper Bulgar]] (Prim Mper Bulgar tl 919–1018, Segondo Mper Bulgar tl 1185–1396)
* [[Mper Serb]] tl 1346–1371
* [[Zarat de la Ruscia]] tl 1547-1721 (dal 1721 inant l mperadëur dl [[Mper Rus]], ma l titul ''Zar'' univa mpò adurva inant nfin tl [[1917]].) 


